title: Tyler Baltierra Calls ‘Teen Mom’ Viewers What?!
text:
Tyler Baltierra Calls ‘Teen Mom’ Viewers What?! Jan 3, 2017 at 11:05 am |   Is Tyler Baltierra crazy? 
Celebrities get a lot of hate online. Especially reality television stars. A lot of the Teen Mom stars are highly criticized for their life choices and bad parenting. Tyler Baltierra and Catelynn Lowell are no exception. Tyler shares exactly what he thinks about Teen Mom fans and their opinions. Check out what he had to say. I don’t think his fans would appreciate this very much. Advertisement
